<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>You agreed to pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b><i>[policy number]&nbsp;</i></b>through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>As no payments have been made,&nbsp;<b>we have cancelled your insurance policy from the date of inception&nbsp;<i>[inception date]</i></b>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br><u>You are now no longer able to claim under this policy, so please disregard any previous documentation you have received from us as null and void.</u><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Since your insurance policy has been cancelled,&nbsp;<u>we want to ensure you're aware that your business may not be covered against claims if you don't have another insurance policy in place.&nbsp;</u><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>It is possible to open a new business insurance policy with the sales team at Kingsbridge, however please be aware this cover cannot be back-dated, which may leave you with a gap in cover.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Please call us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;if you would like to discuss this matter further.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>